  <summary>11/19/2013--Introduced.
Recognizes that additional focus, research, and resources are needed to overcome Alzheimer's disease.

Acknowledges the impact that Alzheimer's disease has on individuals with the disease, their caregivers and loved ones, and the United States.

Expresses support for the goals and implementation of the National Alzheimer's Project Act and the National Plan to Address Alzheimer's Disease.</summary>
